    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_5133921689967639617.png",
                "id": "talent69472",
                "key": "Invoker's Spear",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Invoker's Spear"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>. Level \"Indwelling\" <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span> +1.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai</span>: Memperoleh 1 Level Indwelling. Jika level Indwelling minimum Lv. 8, maka level Indwelling -6.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Berdasarkan Level Indwelling, mendapatkan efek berikut ini</span>:</p><p>Jika Lv. 2 atau lebih: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG </span>yang diakibatkan diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>;<br>Jika Lv. 4 atau lebih: Mengakibatkan DMG +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/c5f5c789f46baf1c0c0ff52d5feabe9a_6073345957213580142.png",
                "id": "talent47691",
                "key": "Secret Rite: Chasmic Soulfarer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Secret Rite: Chasmic Soulfarer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 4 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>. Level \"Indwelling\" <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span> +2.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai</span>: Memperoleh 1 Level Indwelling. Jika level Indwelling minimum Lv. 8, maka level Indwelling -6.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Berdasarkan Level Indwelling, mendapatkan efek berikut ini</span>:</p><p>Jika Lv. 2 atau lebih: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG </span>yang diakibatkan diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>;<br>Jika Lv. 4 atau lebih: Mengakibatkan DMG +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/b6ab0891aede70ddf48bfa3859de14ea_1197043828983985484.png",
                "id": "talent47680",
                "key": "Sacred Rite: Wolf's Swiftness",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sacred Rite: Wolf's Swiftness"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Saat pertandingan dimulai, Karakter ini memperoleh <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pactsworn Pathclearer</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai</span>: Memperoleh 1 Level Indwelling. Jika level Indwelling minimum Lv. 8, maka level Indwelling -6.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Berdasarkan Level Indwelling, mendapatkan efek berikut ini</span>:</p><p>Jika Lv. 2 atau lebih: <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG </span>yang diakibatkan diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>;<br>Jika Lv. 4 atau lebih: Mengakibatkan DMG +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/25750596/8a173f8df2e58a9df74a6c3a74d385eb_7418412509615919494.png",
                "id": "talent99468",
                "key": "Lawful Enforcer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lawful Enforcer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Electro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/19/25750596/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8049930494948734363.png",
                "id": "talent50473",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_2605375576643170880.png",
